    "body": "<!-- markdownlint-disable -->\n\n## Purpose\nFix num_q_heads on DCP for Flashinfer backends\nIn current DCP code for Flashinfer, the `num_qo_heads` is repeatedly multiplied by `dcp_world_size`.\n\n## Test Result\nAlthough it does not affect the precision of inference, sometimes it causes share memory issues. After fixing this bug, the issue can be mitigated.\n",
